#: ../../source/index.rst:34
msgid ""
"They get an address of the form ftp.\\ *<country code>*\\.debian.org "
"(e.g. ftp.us.debian.org). These are the best advertised and most used "
"sites; the face of Debian for most people. See :doc:`official-mirror`."
msgstr ""
"They get an address of the form ftp.\\ *<国コード>*\\.debian.org (例: "
"ftp.jp.debian.org). These are the best advertised and most used sites; "
"多くの人にとって Debian の顔となっています。:doc:`official-mirror` を参照してください。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:41
msgid "Mirror redirector service"
msgstr "ミラーリダイレクトサービス"

#: ../../source/index.rst:42
msgid ""
"If you don't know which mirror to use or your system moves around a lot, "
"you can use the `mirror redirector service <https://deb.debian.org/>`_ in"
" your `/etc/apt/sources.list "
"<http://manpages.debian.org/man/5/sources.list>`_ file."
msgstr ""
"どのミラーを使えばいいのかわからない、あるいは頻繁にシステムを移動する場合は、`ミラーリダイレクトサービス "
"<https://deb.debian.org/>`_ を使えます。`/etc/apt/sources.list "
"<http://manpages.debian.org/man/5/sources.list>`_ ファイルに以下のように記載してください。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:50
msgid ""
"It dynamically redirects package download requests to the best mirror "
"available based on a number of factors such as mirror availability, "
"location, architecture and freshness."
msgstr ""

